Maintainer: Yixian Fan <yixianfan@hust.edu.cn>
Description: We incorporated CRD evaluation algorithm into an open-source R package, named CRDscore, 
             to predict the disruption state of circadian rhythm from single cell or bulk transcriptomic data.
             More about what it does, please see repository for details (https://github.com/yixian-fan/CRDscore). 
